# ─── Ollama (local dev only) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These settings are used by the AI interviewer and exercise hint/review features.
# On Vercel or any cloud host, Ollama is unreachable — AI features will degrade
# gracefully to an error message. Swap in a cloud LLM provider (Gemini, Anthropic)
# in app/api/ai/interview/route.ts and app/api/ai/exercise/route.ts when ready.

OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434
OLLAMA_INTERVIEW_MODEL=qwen2.5:14b
OLLAMA_NUM_CTX=4096

# Tip: set this in your shell profile so two models can't co-load:
# export OLLAMA_MAX_LOADED_MODELS=1
